32180687a83ae322def4a1f050b21df12af12dc7.query: UPDATE __meta SET start_block_height = $1, last_processed_block_height = $1 WHERE indexer_id = $2

5ce34cda52a7f85a2529c0e1c23091e43986d0dd.query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS __meta (
    indexer_id                  text            PRIMARY KEY,
    indexer_type                text            NOT NULL,
    indexer_started_at          timestamptz     NOT NULL,
    last_processed_block_height numeric(20, 0)  NOT NULL,
    start_block_height          numeric(20, 0)  NOT NULL
)

6b8e325869fbe0e5fe649145e580ea13779a015f.query:
INSERT INTO __meta (indexer_id, indexer_type, indexer_started_at, last_processed_block_height, start_block_height)
VALUES ($1, $2, now(), $3, $3)

9c37c7131df3bef3ef2c7008387589af1c785660.query: SELECT last_processed_block_height FROM __meta WHERE indexer_id = $1 LIMIT 1
